title: EP.35: PACKERS VS STEELERS, CANELO'S LOSS, CHRIS PAUL, WIN/LOSS PREDICTIONS, AND MUCH MORE!
description: In this episode we look at both of our favorite NFL teams (Packers and Steelers) and compare them to each other, also predicting our wins and losses from the 2022 opponents. Canelo lost his first fight since Mayweather and we talk about why. Tune in to find out more.
dc:creator: Griffin Proctor & Joe Jokonya
